1-Change the execution to tez or spark
2-Using Suitable file formats like Avro,Parquet or ORC
3-Hive Partitioning
4-Bucketing
5-Vectorization in hive
6-Cost Based Optimization in hive
7-Keeping the Data in Denormalized way to avoid joins
8-Hive Indexing
9-Using Static Partitioning instead of Dynamic if possible
10-Using Compression techniques which reduces disk seeks
11-Map side join
12-Bucket map side join
13-Sort Merge Bucket join
14-Using less number of join columns while doing join so that less number of map reduce jobs are triggered
15-Use sort by instead of order by
16-Use window functions for complex operations
